msgid "策略参数:"
msgstr "策略參數:"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:5
msgid "``sort_ascending``: ``enum``, 是否升序排列因子"
msgstr "``sort_ascending``: ``enum``, 是否升序排列因子"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:7
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:33 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:33
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:32
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:33
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:32
msgid "``True``: 优先选择因子最小的股票,"
msgstr "``True``: 優先選擇因子最小的股票,"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:9
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:35 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:35
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:34
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:35
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:34
msgid "``False``, 优先选择因子最大的股票"
msgstr "``False``, 優先選擇因子最大的股票"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:11
msgid "``weighting``: ``enum``, 股票仓位分配比例权重"
msgstr "``weighting``: ``enum``, 股票倉位分配比例權重"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:13
msgid "``even``       :默认值, 所有被选中的股票都获得同样的权重"
msgstr "``even``       :默認值, 所有被選中的股票都獲得同樣的權重"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:15
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:41 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:41
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:40
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:41
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:40
msgid "``linear``     :权重根据因子排序线性分配"
msgstr "``linear``     :權重根據因子排序線性分配"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:17
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:43 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:43
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:42
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:43
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:42
msgid "``distance``   :股票的权重与他们的指标与最低之间的差值（距离）成比例"
msgstr "``distance``   :股票的權重與他們的指標與最低之間的差值（距離）成比例"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:19
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:45 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:45
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:44
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:45
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:44
msgid "``proportion`` :权重与股票的因子分值成正比"
msgstr "``proportion`` :權重與股票的因子分值成正比"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:21
msgid "``condition``: enum, 股票筛选条件"
msgstr "``condition``: enum, 股票篩選條件"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:23
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:17 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:17
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:16
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:17
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:16
msgid "``any``        :默认值，选择所有可用股票"
msgstr "``any``        :默認值，選擇所有可用股票"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:25
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:19 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:19
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:18
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:19
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:18
msgid "``greater``    :筛选出因子大于``ubound``的股票"
msgstr "``greater``    :篩選出因子大於``ubound``的股票"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:27
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:21 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:21
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:20
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:21
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:20
msgid "``less``       :筛选出因子小于``lbound``的股票"
msgstr "``less``       :篩選出因子小於``lbound``的股票"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:29
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:23 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:23
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:22
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:23
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:22
msgid "``between``    :筛选出因子介于``lbound``与``ubound``之间的股票"
msgstr "``between``    :篩選出因子介於``lbound``與``ubound``之間的股票"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:31
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:25 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:25
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:24
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:25
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:24
msgid "``not_between``:筛选出因子不在``lbound``与``ubound``之间的股票"
msgstr "``not_between``:篩選出因子不在``lbound``與``ubound``之間的股票"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:33
msgid "``lbound``: ``float``, 股票筛选下限值, 默认值``np.-inf``"
msgstr "``lbound``: ``float``, 股票篩選下限值, 默認值``np.-inf``"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:35
msgid "``ubound``: ``float``, 股票筛选上限值, 默认值``np.inf``"
msgstr "``ubound``: ``float``, 股票篩選上限值, 默認值``np.inf``"

